{"tid":971711,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「中非打」如果環保撚下一步咁做","createTime":"2019-01-07T00:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T09:49:41.000Z","uid":150465,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a642afe6e8b60e1f6755c893443b6a610eb18c71","tid":971711,"uid":150465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T00:11:38.000Z","msg":"啲食肆會主動提供返飲筒俾顧客 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然之後同你講：「拎走你地飲筒已經嘈到咁，諗下啲熱帶雨林嘅動物成個森林俾人類斬咗啊！你地游水都唔想個泳池有任何一點污染啦！」<br />\n<br />\n或者<br />\n：「動物佢地無得揀，但係我地人類仲有得揀。」<br />\n<br />\n咁講之後成件事會唔會soft啲容易接受咗？<br />\n利申：中非打，純粹覺得件事咁發展會幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4b0eca252cdea89f6ac5eec3170f2d4f00314c","tid":971711,"uid":48796,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T00:38:21.000Z","msg":"點解要附和班環保撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n海龜鼻插飲管, 根本問題係點解垃圾會漂出大海, 一個城巿正正常常處理垃圾點會去咗大海 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134a95ed90e366779e5945d8913b2633df86225a","tid":971711,"uid":150465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f4b0eca252cdea89f6ac5eec3170f2d4f00314c","tid":971711,"uid":48796,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T00:38:21.000Z","msg":"點解要附和班環保撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n海龜鼻插飲管, 根本問題係點解垃圾會漂出大海, 一個城巿正正常常處理垃圾點會去咗大海 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:29:29.000Z","msg":"咁又係，佢地呢種老土嘅手段的確係唔多好，利用人偽善嘅行為（見到動物受傷就識心痛）去做呼籲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n但係走塑唔單單係為咗個海污染嘅，仲會引發其他問題，可能係未來發展都要面對嘅問題，係種大趨勢啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每一個幾輕微選擇都會影響到未來嘅發展<br />\n<br />\n環保即使唔係為生態，都係講緊嘅係未來嘅人類發展，而喺香港同人講未來係咪太奢侈呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a209c056ca212585f56329671c545c9e7c371ec","tid":971711,"uid":150465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:31:10.000Z","msg":"純粹理性討論，唔係想引戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c671884b96398fa2759760817d5bef3fd6105748","tid":971711,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"134a95ed90e366779e5945d8913b2633df86225a","tid":971711,"uid":150465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f4b0eca252cdea89f6ac5eec3170f2d4f00314c","tid":971711,"uid":48796,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T00:38:21.000Z","msg":"點解要附和班環保撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n海龜鼻插飲管, 根本問題係點解垃圾會漂出大海, 一個城巿正正常常處理垃圾點會去咗大海 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:29:29.000Z","msg":"咁又係，佢地呢種老土嘅手段的確係唔多好，利用人偽善嘅行為（見到動物受傷就識心痛）去做呼籲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n但係走塑唔單單係為咗個海污染嘅，仲會引發其他問題，可能係未來發展都要面對嘅問題，係種大趨勢啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<